{"tid":980012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港機管局：去年旅客、飛機起降量及貨運總量均上升","createTime":"2019-01-13T07:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T07:38:25.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2f1763742bc305bac00e200c1d096083b85564","tid":980012,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"機管局表示，去年機場接待旅客達7470萬人次，飛機起降量達42萬7725架次，分別按年上升2.5%和1.7%。貨運總量亦達510萬公噸，比同期增加1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n單計去年12月，飛機起降量達37085架次，客運量達653萬人次，比2017年同期分別按年增加1.2%和1.7%。貨運量則有44萬8000公噸，較前年同期下降5.2%。<br />\n<br />\n機管局解釋，12月的客運增幅主要受到訪港旅客和本港居民外遊人數上升所帶動。至於貨運量減少則受到全球經濟環境不明朗的因素影響。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437833-20190113.htm?share=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437833-20190113.htm%3Fshare%3Dfacebook&d=QbdtIZsqsWgwJ28ExpSMKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=347ad1ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437833-20190113.htm%3Fshare%3Dfacebook&h=1e7d0991\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437833-20190113.htm?share=facebook</a>"}]}